['
', '   \item Given parallelogram $ABCD$ with $m\angle A=55^\circ$, $AB=8$, and $BC=5$. Find the value of each angle measure and side length.
', '   \begin{multicols}{2}
', '     \begin{enumerate}
', '       \item $m\angle B=$\vspace{0.5cm}
', '       \item $m\angle C=$\vspace{0.5cm}
